text: Patricia Obregón was an archer from Costa Rica. She was born on 18 February 1952 and died on 6 October 2020. Obregón competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics.Patricia ObregónPatricia OBREGON == References == Category:1952 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Costa Rican archers Category:Olympians for Costa Rica Category:Sportspeople from San José, Costa Rica
